The oath of office shall be administered by the President of the Senate to each Senator who shall be elected, previous to his taking his seat.
(R.S. § 28.)

Editorial Notes
Codification
R.S. § 28 derived from act June 1, 1789, ch. 1, § 2, 1 Stat. 23.</akn:p></akn:content></akn:section></akn:body></akn:act></akn:akomaNtoso>